TY  - JOUR
TI  - Equilibrium with Transaction Costs
AU  - Hahn, F. H.
AB  - [This paper examines some of the modifications required in well known propositions of general equilibrium theory when transactions require resources. Some preliminary remarks on the analysis of money in such economies are also offered.]
