TY  - JOUR
TI  - Estimating a Structural Equation in a Large System
AU  - Fisher, Walter D.
AU  - Wadycki, Walter J.
AB  - [In two stage least squares estimation, when the matrix Z of predetermined variables has less than full column rank, Z′Z is singular. It is shown that in this situation 2SLS still can be used and that Ŷ - the result of the first stage--is still uniquely determined; also shown is that 2SLS will often be equivalent to OLS.]
