TY  - JOUR
TI  - Shiftable versus Non-Shiftable Capital: A Synthesis
AU  - Weitzman, Martin L.
AB  - [Non-transferable capital is an essential feature of the Fel'dman two-sector growth model. This paper is primarily an answer to the following question. Given that capital is really partially shiftable between its two sectors, when can the Fel'dman model be meaningfully used?]
